00:11.220 --> 00:13.020
- What do you mean,
she hit on you?

00:13.020 --> 00:14.110
- Well, she--

00:14.110 --> 00:15.160
- While she's the judge
on your case?

00:15.160 --> 00:17.070
- She was going
to recuse herself,

00:17.070 --> 00:18.220
and then she thought
it would have no effect.

00:18.220 --> 00:20.020
- Does this just happen?

00:20.020 --> 00:21.160
Women come up to you

00:21.160 --> 00:23.020
