that's my problem.

00:32.189 --> 00:34.090
- Since when did you take
such a strong interest

00:34.090 --> 00:35.160
in math, Ellenor?

00:35.160 --> 00:37.080
- Certain equations
fascinate me.

00:37.080 --> 00:39.010
- Try adding two plus two.

00:39.010 --> 00:40.190
