with your asbestos clients.

00:40.190 --> 00:42.100
- Is this what happens to women
when you insert your penis?

00:42.100 --> 00:43.210
I'm just curious,
because they become...

00:43.210 --> 00:44.210
- Hey!
- Greedy little--

00:44.210 --> 00:47.040
- Lindsay!

00:47.040 --> 00:48.110
- What's going on, Leonard?

00:48.110 --> 00:50.000
- I'm not feeling too good.

00:50.000 --> 00:52.140
