- Oh, God.

00:52.140 --> 00:55.230
I'm practically getting
a contact high off your breath.

00:55.230 --> 00:57.110
- Why do you keep
defending this guy?

00:57.110 --> 00:58.230
- Because I like him,

00:58.230 --> 01:00.090
because he was
my first client ever,

01:00.090 --> 01:01.150
and because he's innocent.

01:01.150 --> 01:02.200
- On the count of possession

01:02.200 --> 01:04.099
of a controlled substance,

01:04.099 --> 01:07.070
we find the defendant
not guilty.

01:07.070 --> 01:09.210
