with the thanks of the Court.

01:09.210 --> 01:13.200
- You did it.
MAN: We're adjourned.

01:13.200 --> 01:15.230
- It means nothing, Leonard,
if you don't get help.

01:15.230 --> 01:17.070
- Why do you care so much?

01:17.070 --> 01:18.230
