you get to meet good people.

01:22.070 --> 01:23.110
- This I know.

01:27.140 --> 01:28.160
- I had a really good time
last night.

01:28.160 --> 01:31.050
- Me too.

01:31.050 --> 01:32.160
So do you want to come
to the game tonight?

01:32.160 --> 01:33.190
- Is that tonight?

01:33.190 --> 01:35.030
- Yeah.
- Cool.

01:35.030 --> 01:37.110
- So, I'll call you
this afternoon?

01:37.110 --> 01:38.120
- Okay.

01:38.120 --> 01:40.000
- Between now and then,

01:40.000 --> 01:43.000
