40:58.180 --> 40:59.160
- Come on in.

41:02.180 --> 41:04.060
- Hi.
- Hi.

41:04.060 --> 41:07.040
Wow, some place.

41:07.040 --> 41:09.130
- Yeah, well,
I make a lot of money.

41:12.160 --> 41:16.030
- Listen, I never got a chance
to thank you for defending me.

41:16.030 --> 41:18.110
- I lost the motion.

41:18.110 --> 41:20.040
- Yeah.

41:22.010 --> 41:25.060
- You okay?

41:25.060 --> 41:26.090
What's wrong?

41:26.090 --> 41:27.110
- Nothing, nothing.

41:27.110 --> 41:31.120
It's, uh--

41:31.120 --> 41:34.200
when I think about
why I practice law,

41:34.200 --> 41:36.070
my mind always
goes to the little guy.

41:36.070 --> 41:37.070
You know, the Leonards?

41:37.070 --> 41:39.050
The people that I fight for?

41:39.050 --> 41:41.130
And after ten years,
for him to just sell me out.

41:41.130 --> 41:42.210
- Ellenor,
he's a drug addict.

41:42.210 --> 41:46.200
- No, no, no,
let me finish.

41:46.200 --> 41:48.140
I've been sitting home
for the last two hours

41:48.140 --> 41:50.210
feeling sorry for myself,

41:50.210 --> 41:52.210
thinking that nobody's loyal.

41:52.210 --> 41:56.160
There's just no such thing as--

41:56.160 --> 42:00.170
and then my mind went to

42:00.170 --> 42:02.210
how all of you
stood up for me,

42:02.210 --> 42:06.160
dropped everything.

42:08.200 --> 42:12.210
I'm sorry for the way
I've treated you lately.

42:12.210 --> 42:18.100
I think this whole partnership
thing has blinded me to--

42:18.100 --> 42:20.030
I don't know,
to what it really means

42:20.030 --> 42:23.170
to have true partners.

42:23.170 --> 42:26.120
I know I have them.

42:26.120 --> 42:29.090
I especially know
you're one of them.

42:32.080 --> 42:34.040
- Thank you.

42:34.040 --> 42:37.040
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

42:37.040 --> 42:41.150
<i>♪ ♪</i>

42:41.150 --> 42:46.210
- Well,
that's all I came to say.

42:46.210 --> 42:48.190
See you at work.
- Okay.
